 Colin Powell
(I)


 
Actor





Colin Powell was born on April 5, 1937 in New York City, New York, USA as Colin Luther Powell. He is an actor, known for Breath of Freedom (2014), For Love of Liberty: The Story of America's Black Patriots (2010) and Janet: The Velvet Rope (1998). He has been married to Alma Powell since August 25, 1962. They have three children.            
See full bio »
            
 


